p.k: Darwin is too polite to speak his mind, so Gumball teaches him to be direct. / Carrie takes Gumball, Darwin and Anais to a real haunted house party on Halloween. / Gumball, Darwin, and Anais search for the Watterson family treasure. / Richard gets a job as a pizza delivery man, which worries Nicole when, at the same time, strange things begin to occur around the neighbourhood. / Darwin develops a texting addiction when he and Gumball get their first cell phone. / Gumball seeks justice when Banana Joe chews Darwin's pen. / Gumball is determined to drive Penny away from Leslie / When everyone in the Watterson household wants to watch their favourite show at the same time, a massive fight breaks out over control of the television remote. / Nicole seeks to develop a sense of ambition in Gumball
